abstract: >-
  Horosa for Windows v2.2.0 beta is a local-first metaphysics workstation that aligns the
  latest Mac-side work (two new 数算 methods — 邵子参评数 / 河洛理数; harmonic (调波) chart rendering; a full React rewrite of the Feng Shui 纳气盘; AI model-selection hardening; plus prior Ollama-streaming, BaZi/Taiyi/PD, Qimen and clean-machine fixes) and AI Analysis rework, astrology modules, traditional Chinese methods,
  kentang/kin backend integrations, AI-assisted structured export, Python and Java
  services, and self-contained Windows desktop delivery into one cross-platform
  release line.

